      "IPI ran a field intelligence operation on polio eradication in conflict zones, Pakistan, Afghanistan, Nigeria, Somalia, through a researcher named Nasra Hassan. Her reports went to IPI's Vienna office, then to Rød-Larsen, then to Epstein. The Gates Foundation was the funder. By February 2015 the chain was explicit: Hassan sent Rød-Larsen a Pakistan update marked \"Urgent, Confi\" with the instruction \"plz pass on to Bill Gates.\" It went to Epstein first.",
      "Nigeria was the most active thread. November 2013: Boko Haram had attacked polio workers in Kano. A northern Nigerian group was calling on President Jonathan to suspend Gates's planned visit. Rød-Larsen forwarded the report to Epstein. December 2013: IPI researcher Mark Shaw sent a two-page intelligence brief, \"what we are hearing at multiple levels,\" about polio obstruction. It went to IPI director Andrea Pfanzelter, then Rød-Larsen, then Epstein. June 2014: IPI's formal reports on barriers to polio eradication in Nigeria and Somalia were forwarded to Epstein. Classified research on Nigerian security conditions, routed through a convicted sex offender to the world's largest private foundation.",
