      "Maxwell avait d\u00e9j\u00e0 explor\u00e9 la logistique. Elle fit son rapport \u00e0 Epstein le lendemain apr\u00e8s avoir parl\u00e9 au bureau de Richardson\u00a0: \"it is a trip pre some sort of presedential running announcement - not state sponsored, not UN sanctioned - he is hoping to be invoted by Chad govt (not confimed yet) he is flying to Kartoum because you can't fly to darfur as it is too dangerous. US embassy will arrange for a flight from Kartoum to Darfur where he will meet w/anyone who'll meet w/him\" (cf909a32874bbd0ba7fd3561886e0527-0). Elle signala le risque\u00a0: \"not un or us sanctioned so no real protection for the plane or pilots.\"",
      "Epstein ne s'en \u00e9mut pas. \"I'll call him,\" \u00e9crivit-il. \"He is old friend of the sudanese presidnt however\" (cf909a32874bbd0ba7fd3561886e0527-0). Le pr\u00e9sident soudanais \u00e9tait Omar el-B\u00e9chir, plus tard inculp\u00e9 par la Cour p\u00e9nale internationale pour g\u00e9nocide au Darfour.",
      "Maxwell insista sur la s\u00e9curit\u00e9. \"TW sd he is interested in the trip but only if he can understand and feel safe about security - what type of plane fly from kartoum to darfur - what security do we have on the trip what security on the ground.\" Elle ajouta\u00a0: \"I'd love to go but given no un and not govt sponsored trip security is a key question - life is cheap out there.\" Epstein lui dit de \"talk to bill about your concerns\" (cf909a32874bbd0ba7fd3561886e0527-0).",
      "Le 31 d\u00e9cembre, Maxwell avait pris sa d\u00e9cision. \"TW I don't think will do trip,\" \u00e9crivit-elle, \"but if you are going to pay for part of the charter then I probably would go w/Pat\" (2d10603b4028a195b05ab3cd7569a15a-0). Trois jours plus tard, le prix arriva. Janis Hartley, directrice de l'agenda au bureau du gouverneur Bill Richardson, \u00e9crivit directement \u00e0 Maxwell\u00a0: \"Ghislaine -- Half the price of a charter plane to Khartoum would be around $183,000. Is this possible?\" R\u00e9ponse d'Epstein \u00e0 Maxwell\u00a0: \"have him call me today!!\" (d1a5370b6715ae20b2b3fbd4d68d381d-0).",
      "Aucun email des archives ne confirme que le voyage ait eu lieu. Richardson annon\u00e7a sa campagne pr\u00e9sidentielle le 21 janvier 2007. Il fut ensuite nomm\u00e9 secr\u00e9taire \u00e0 l'\u00c9nergie par Obama avant de se retirer face \u00e0 une enqu\u00eate du grand jury sur des accusations de corruption. En 2008, une femme porta plainte pour attouchement lors d'une soir\u00e9e. Richardson mourut en septembre 2023, quelques mois apr\u00e8s avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 nomm\u00e9 dans les documents civils li\u00e9s \u00e0 Epstein.",
